48cc70456eb01527af9170da72519b2fc0636cee071b997af973e99195aa97941dac8fae560d88722e6f991dd3188f1887a2bba8bdd0b5ab5f314af93e95f2d7  0001-Fix-open_memstream-fmemopen-feature-detection-with-G.patch
